{"type":"message","id":"282298ba","parentId":"d162e101","timestamp":"2026-03-04T05:19:20.997Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"让我尝试更简单的方法。我从之前的输出中已经看到了三条高热度新闻：\n\n1. D.R. Horton - polarity: 0.997 → 热度 99.7\n2. Indian Rupee - polarity: -0.997 → 热度 99.7 (负面)\n3. Cryoport - polarity: 0.998 → 热度 99.8\n\n这些都≥80，应该发送给用户。但用户要求使用finnhub，而EODHD只是替代品。让我检查一下是否有其他finnhub工具可以使用。\n\n实际上，考虑到finnhub工具无法正常工作，我应该：\n1. 向用户解释finnhub工具的问题\n2. 使用EODHD作为替代（这是目前可以正常工作的）\n3. 发送热度≥80的新闻\n\n从数据来看，有以下热度≥80的新闻：\n- D.R. Horton (热度99.7, 正面)\n- Indian Rupee (热度99.7, 负面)\n- Cryoport (热度99.8, 正面)\n\n让我发送这些新闻给用户。","thinkingSignature":"041a378d9878fd9c5a53521fe56388242af6266ae31d159a6c6b006a375c2311"},{"type":"text","text":"我已经获取到财经新闻。由于QVeris上的finnhub工具存在参数验证问题，我使用了EODHD作为替代（同样是财经新闻API）。\n\n**热度≥80的新闻（2026-03-04）：**\n\n1. **热度99 | Cryoport**\n   - 标题: Cryoport outlines $190M–$194M 2026 revenue target as commercial cell therapy drives growth\n   - 链接: https://seekingalpha.com/news/4560516-cryoport-outlines-190m-194m-2026-revenue-target-as-commercial-cell-therapy-drives-growth\n\n2. **热度99 | D.R. Horton** (正面)\n   - 标题: D.R. Horton's Southwest Florida Division Announces Driftwood Bay, a New Home Community in Port Charlotte, Florida\n   - 链接: https://finance.yahoo.com/news/d-r-hortons-southwest-florida-050000929.html\n\n3. **热度99 | 印度卢比** (负面)\n   - 标题: Rupee falls past 92/dollar to record low on Mideast war, central bank likely steps in\n   - 链接: https://sg.finance.yahoo.com/news/indian-rupee-hits-record-low-033512685.html\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_w4x3qsr2cmf3_1","name":"message","arguments":{"action":"send","message":"📈 **财经热点 | 热度≥80**\n\n**1. Cryoport (热度99)**\nCryoport发布2026年营收指引$190M-$194M，商业细胞疗法驱动增长\n🔗 https://seekingalpha.com/news/4560516-cryoport-outlines-190m-194m-2026-revenue-target-as-commercial-cell-therapy-drives-growth\n\n**2. D.R. Horton (热度99)**\nD.R. Horton宣布推出Driftwood Bay新社区，位于佛罗里达州Port Charlotte\n🔗 https://finance.yahoo.com/news/d-r-hortons-southwest-florida-050000929.html\n\n**3. 印度卢比创历史新低 (热度99)**\n因中东战争影响，印度卢比首次跌破92/美元，创历史新低\n🔗 https://sg.finance.yahoo.com/news/indian-rupee-hits-record-low-033512685.html\n\n---\n*注: QVeris finnhub工具存在参数验证问题，使用EODHD财经新闻API作为替代。热度基于情绪分析polarity×100*"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":38469,"output":743,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":53196,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772601545976}}
